description:
Check out the collaboration pack between Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL and Oshiribeat, the multi-genre content creator group!

This DLC includes a total of 7 new songs.

New Songs
1. Bossfire - Roy Mikelate (feat. ATAS)
2. OMOIDE - Essbee
3. Le Petit Princess - Plastic Fruits
4. Diosa maquinaria - MASEraaaN
5. SPECTRUM - Essbee
6. Sanity - K-forest
7. SLECTA - mybear
name: Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL - Oshiribeat Pack
